cross: Sarcochilus Kulnura Spice x Sarcochilus Sweetheart

measurements.description: Thirty-eight full flowers and 25 buds on six upright inflorescences up to 21.5cm; sepals and petals white, marked medium burgundy basally, light burgundy edges; lip white, midlobe marked dark yellow, sidelobes marked burgundy; anther cap white; substance hard; texture slightly crystalline.
